items.title: Awesome Vite

*   [rollup-plugin-i18next-dts-gen (⭐83)](https://github.com/rxliuli/liuli-tools/tree/master/libs/rollup-plugin-i18next-dts-gen) - Generating type definitions from i18n JSON files are used for code hinting and validation.
